data.description: Charming Montecito Villa condo which has been well maintained & it shows. Tile & carpet flooring, great room, high ceilings through out, open kitchen with granite counter tops, 2 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, 2 car attached garage, balcony & best of all a community pool to enjoy the sunny California weather. So what are you waiting for, schedule an appointment to see this property today before it's gone.
